title: Rosebud
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Greek
description: Cafe bar with occasional live music. Vegan choices include a mille feuille with beets and hummus, broccoli soup, quiona with cream of pepper, linguini with saffron and wakame seaweed, veggie burger. Bright and colorful space with free Wi-Fi.
